Certainly! Below are the 7-day and 14-day email drafts, adapted to match the structure of the 3-day version.


---

7-Day Email Notification

Subject: [IMPORTANT]: ACTION REQUIRED - Pull Request Pending for Over 7 Days in Repository {repo_name}

To: [Manager's Name]

Cc: [VP1's Name]


---

Why You Are Receiving This Email:

To integrate SonarQube across all repositories and ensure consistent code quality standards across the various technologies used within the enterprise, a pull request in the repository "{repo_name}" has remained open for more than 7 days and requires immediate attention.


---

ACTION REQUIRED:

The pull request in the repository "{repo_name}" has been pending for more than 7 days.

Immediate action is required to prevent delays.



---

Details:

Repository: {repo_name}

Pull Request Age: More than 7 days


Next Steps:

1. Review the pull request and take the necessary actions.


2. Address any required changes or approve it promptly.



Note: VP1 is included in this email for escalation purposes.


---

What Happens Next?

If no action is taken in the next 7 days, the matter will be escalated to VP2 for urgent intervention.



---

Where Can You Obtain Assistance?

Email: Please reach out to sonarqube-alerts@example.com for questions or further assistance.

Slack: Join the discussion on #sonarqube_support.

Documentation: Refer to our SonarQube Integration Guide for more details on handling pull requests.



---

Thank you for your immediate attention.

[Your Team Name]


---

14-Day Email Notification

Subject: [CRITICAL]: URGENT ACTION REQUIRED - Pull Request Overdue in Repository {repo_name}

To: [VP2's Name]


---

Why You Are Receiving This Email:

To integrate SonarQube across all repositories and ensure consistent code quality standards across the various technologies used within the enterprise, a pull request in the repository "{repo_name}" has remained open for over 14 days without resolution. This delay is causing significant risk to project timelines.


---

ACTION REQUIRED:

The pull request in the repository "{repo_name}" has been overdue for more than 14 days and requires urgent action.

Please intervene to expedite the resolution.



---

Details:

Repository: {repo_name}

Pull Request Age: Over 14 days


Next Steps:

1. Review the status of the pull request and initiate the necessary actions for resolution.


2. Escalate within your teams if required to ensure prompt completion.




---

Where Can You Obtain Assistance?

Email: Please reach out to sonarqube-alerts@example.com for questions or further assistance.

Slack: Join the discussion on #sonarqube_support.

Documentation: Refer to our SonarQube Integration Guide for more details on handling pull requests.



---

Thank you for addressing this matter urgently.

[Your Team Name]


---

These templates follow the escalation hierarchy you specified: the 7-day email notifies the manager with VP1 in CC, and the 14-day email directly involves VP2. Let me know if any other changes are needed.

